snippet.title: Diablo Immortal | Release Date & PC Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
On June 2, Evil is everywhere.

Diablo Immortal is a free-to-play game coming to iOS, Android and PC Open Beta.

Pre-register: https://www.DiabloImmortal.com
